title: Khon Kaen Provincial Administrative Organization Stadium
text: Khon Kaen Provincial Administrative Organization Stadium () is a <a href="multi-purpose%20stadium">multi-purpose stadium</a> in <a href="Khon%20Kaen%20Province">Khon Kaen Province</a> , <a href="Thailand">Thailand</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home stadium of <a href="Khon%20Kaen%20F.C.">Khon Kaen F.C.</a> and <a href="Khon%20Kaen%20United%20F.C.">Khon Kaen United</a>. The stadium holds 7,000 people.
